1
00:00:00,580 --> 00:00:02,839
Would you help me then?

2
00:00:02,839 --> 00:00:05,920
What? You want me to help?

3
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:07,130
Well...

4
00:00:07,130 --> 00:00:09,880
Why? You don't me want to?

5
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:13,400
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

6
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,400
♫ <i> No matter how sad my voice is, you keep your poker face</i> ♫

7
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:19,590
<i> [Episode 2]
 [My Crush is Flirting With Another Girl]</i>

8
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,440
Hi.

9
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:32,400
Excuse me. Where did you get transferred from?

10
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:34,800
You probably wouldn't know it, even if I told you.

11
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,819
Should I bring textbooks to you from the teacher's office?

12
00:00:36,819 --> 00:00:39,736
No, thank you. I'll bring them later.

13
00:00:39,736 --> 00:00:42,716
Do you like going to coin karaoke?

14
00:00:42,716 --> 00:00:44,440
Hey.

15
00:00:45,660 --> 00:00:48,140
My name Yang Hyeji...

16
00:00:48,140 --> 00:00:49,460
What?

17
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:53,660
What?

18
00:00:53,660 --> 00:00:55,640
Hi, Yuho.

19
00:00:56,780 --> 00:00:59,200
Oh, hi.

20
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,840
But, do you know me?

21
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,240
Yes. I know you.

22
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,130
I've heard a lot about you.

23
00:01:04,130 --> 00:01:05,980
From who?

24
00:01:08,820 --> 00:01:11,220
From one of my friends.

25
00:01:11,220 --> 00:01:13,490
Hyeji, you should keep tabs on her.

26
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:14,600
What?

27
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:17,216
This might be where your one-sided crush ends.

28
00:01:17,216 --> 00:01:19,040
You must want to end your life right here.

29
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:21,696
Eunah, we should help her with that.

30
00:01:21,696 --> 00:01:23,599
What? "Do you like going to coin karaoke?"

31
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:26,240
You want me to beat you up at a coin karaoke?!

32
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:31,360
Do they know each other?

33
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:35,860
You know, that girl who transferred?

34
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:37,976
Youngji? What about her?

35
00:01:37,976 --> 00:01:41,280
You are prettier. There's no comparison.

36
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:44,216
Well, I think I have seen her before.

37
00:01:44,216 --> 00:01:46,696
- Where? 
 - No idea.

38
00:01:46,696 --> 00:01:50,036
I don't know, but I think I have seen her. There's something familiar about her.

39
00:01:50,036 --> 00:01:52,259
Well, you must be mistaken.

40
00:01:52,259 --> 00:01:54,179
She transferred from far away.

41
00:01:54,179 --> 00:01:55,950
Really?

42
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:58,300
But, more importantly,

43
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:01,096
I think she knows Yuho.

44
00:02:01,096 --> 00:02:03,516
No way, she has just transferred.

45
00:02:03,516 --> 00:02:07,360
You're right. Anyway, they didn't look close to each other.

46
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:10,659
That...

47
00:02:10,659 --> 00:02:13,120
They look close.

48
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,960
You can return books here.

49
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,590
Thank you for bringing me here.

50
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,290
I love reading.

51
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:19,840
Really? I have to—

52
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:22,520
Oh, where is the Science room?

53
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:25,600
Oh, the Science room?

54
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,630
That is...

55
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:30,100
Let's go. It's almost time for class to start.

56
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,560
Yeah.

57
00:02:32,216 --> 00:02:34,550
<i>I have done nothing wrong.</i>

58
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:36,840
<i>Why am I the one avoiding them?</i>

59
00:02:42,110 --> 00:02:46,840
Put 3 to the x and the answer is no.2.

60
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,000
Doing it this way is a bit easier.

61
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:52,000
It's hard though.

62
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:55,000
Let's do it again.

63
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,500
Hyeji.

64
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:59,516
That isn't the problem you need to be solving right now.

65
00:02:59,516 --> 00:03:01,740
What are you talking about?

66
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,860
Why? They are just erasing the blackboard.

67
00:03:07,860 --> 00:03:09,530
Oh, really?

68
00:03:09,530 --> 00:03:11,290
They could just be helping each other.

69
00:03:11,290 --> 00:03:12,590
I'm the one assigned to do that today.

70
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,810
Then, you go help them.

71
00:03:13,810 --> 00:03:16,759
Hey, how could I be there between them? Look.

72
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:19,160
They look like a lovely pair.

73
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:22,320
Hyeji, I will go kill them.

74
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:30,460
<i>What is going on there?</i>

75
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:34,320
Thank you for helping me. I am not tall enough to be able to erase up there.

76
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:38,616
- You can. 
 - No, I can't.

77
00:03:38,616 --> 00:03:40,880
Would you erase it up there?

78
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:42,840
Okay.

79
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,840
Clean it.

80
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:47,700
No, here.

81
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:51,470
You are tall.

82
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:53,840
Choi Taeil is the one assigned to do this today.

83
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,980
Just help me this once.

84
00:03:55,980 --> 00:04:01,699
<i>The hard thing about a one-sided crush is that I don't have the right to feel bad and get comforted.</i>

85
00:04:01,699 --> 00:04:03,519
<i>Do you know her?</i>

86
00:04:03,519 --> 00:04:05,460
No. I met her for the first time today.

87
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,880
It didn't look that way.

88
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:09,596
It is her first day at school. She's asking me lots of stuff.

89
00:04:09,596 --> 00:04:12,120
Why was she asking only you?

90
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,160
Are you jealous?

91
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:15,960
No way.

92
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,660
Is it for me?

93
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:20,936
- Thank you. 
 - Give it back, it's not for you.

94
00:04:20,936 --> 00:04:23,120
Then who?

95
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,800
Oh, Hyeji.

96
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:27,420
Oh! Yuho.

97
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:29,290
Have you been to the cafeteria?

98
00:04:29,290 --> 00:04:30,990
Yeah, just now.

99
00:04:30,990 --> 00:04:32,800
Is that an extra?

100
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:35,350
What? Well...

101
00:04:35,350 --> 00:04:38,850
I was just there, but they were out of chocolate milk.

102
00:04:38,850 --> 00:04:41,360
If it's an extra one, I'll buy it from you.

103
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,556
No, it is okay. You can just have it.

104
00:04:43,556 --> 00:04:46,220
Wow, really? Thank you.

105
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:49,800
Oh, wasn't this for Youngji?

106
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:56,840
Yoo! Young! Ji!

107
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,399
Why is it this hard?

108
00:04:58,399 --> 00:05:01,296
How can I solve this problem?

109
00:05:01,296 --> 00:05:03,260
Hyeji, are you okay?

110
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:05,696
What? Why?

111
00:05:05,696 --> 00:05:08,480
Well, you know...

112
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:11,179
Hey, you know. I am always on your side.

113
00:05:11,179 --> 00:05:12,390
Why?

114
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:15,610
This is their first time meeting, and she keeps acting close to him.

115
00:05:15,610 --> 00:05:17,596
She's a little weird.

116
00:05:17,596 --> 00:05:20,680
- Who? 
 - Oh, a girl...

117
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:23,276
She... Dog! 
 <i>(T/N: the words for "she" and "dog" sound similar in Korean)</i>

118
00:05:23,276 --> 00:05:25,270
Taeil's dog!

119
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,900
My dog?

120
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,219
I don't have one.

121
00:05:28,219 --> 00:05:30,740
You do.

122
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,400
I don't.

123
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,920
You should.

124
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:37,700
Hyeji, can I talk to you?

125
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:39,120
What?

126
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:49,530
But...

127
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:52,280
I really don't have any dogs.

128
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:55,456
Why? What are you talking about?

129
00:05:55,456 --> 00:05:58,920
I like cats.

130
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,440
Me, too.

131
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:07,139
I know what you are going to say.

132
00:06:07,139 --> 00:06:08,470
What?

133
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:12,360
I am not that close to Yuho.

134
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,599
There is nothing between us.

135
00:06:14,599 --> 00:06:16,759
Would you help me then?

136
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:19,840
What? You want me to help?

137
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,040
That's a little...

138
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,210
Why? You can't?

139
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:26,060
No, it is not that...

140
00:06:28,180 --> 00:06:30,316
- Okay. 
 - What?

141
00:06:30,316 --> 00:06:32,130
My part-timer is so cute.

142
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:34,200
What are you talking about?

143
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:48,200
<i> Oh, what's going on? </i>

144
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:53,820
<i> Oh?</i>

145
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:56,940
<i> The teacher is doing Tae-bo for no reason!</i>

146
00:07:11,590 --> 00:07:12,820
What's going on?

147
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:15,360
It's me. The witch.

148
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,639
Boss?

149
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:19,856
What do you think? I've changed perfectly, right?

150
00:07:19,856 --> 00:07:22,099
- I am cute, right? 
 - Be quiet.

151
00:07:22,099 --> 00:07:24,136
You asked.

152
00:07:24,136 --> 00:07:27,236
Well, I was just kidding earlier.

153
00:07:27,236 --> 00:07:29,499
You aren't irritated about Yuho, right?

154
00:07:29,499 --> 00:07:32,420
Why are you here?

155
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:35,100
Hyeji, the next class has changed to Life and Ethics.

156
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,530
We should move to another classroom.

157
00:07:36,530 --> 00:07:38,520
Got it. Thank you.

158
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:40,479
See you at the shop later.

159
00:07:40,479 --> 00:07:43,740
Don't do anything. Anything.

160
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,000
Anything!

161
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:53,220
<i> What was she thinking coming all the way to school?</i>

162
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:57,300
<i> I may go to your school to see you.</i>

163
00:07:57,900 --> 00:08:00,700
<i> Wow, she really came.</i>

164
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,540
<i> Hey, can I sit here?</i>

165
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,560
Yes, you can.

166
00:08:19,690 --> 00:08:28,290
♫ <i> It's moving in your direction. 
I don't know where my heart will end up </i> ♫

167
00:08:28,290 --> 00:08:32,450
Following the Korea royal refuge at the Russian legation, King Gojong returned to the palace.

168
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,080
Excuse me.

169
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,630
It's class time right now.

170
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:47,900
Sorry, wake me up after it is over.

171
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:54,460
♫ <i> If you recognize me. 'Cuz far away so lonely night </i> ♫

172
00:08:54,460 --> 00:09:00,760
Stop making sounds with your pen.
